Extracts end point data (last cycle)

krsa_extractEndPoint.Rd

This function takes in raw data and chip type and returns end point data (last cycle)

krsa_extractEndPoint(df, type = c("STK", "PTK"))

Arguments

df

krsa raw tidy data

type

chip type

Value

end point signals df
